532
00:52:37,594 --> 00:52:38,516
Get out of here.

533
00:53:22,002 --> 00:53:23,643
Go, run her over!

534
00:53:38,871 --> 00:53:41,288
-Yeah.
-We tried it your way,

535
00:53:41,288 --> 00:53:42,499
now we'll do it mine.

536
00:53:42,732 --> 00:53:44,879
Bring it...now.

537
00:53:45,002 --> 00:53:45,981
Okay!

538
00:54:37,494 --> 00:54:39,753
Come on, come on! Hold it up!

539
00:54:55,608 --> 00:54:57,548
Now we're going to your brother.

540
00:54:57,573 --> 00:54:58,623
We're too late.

541
00:55:01,217 --> 00:55:02,713
Lara, what are you doing?

542
00:55:14,218 --> 00:55:15,250
Take us up!

543
00:55:19,584 --> 00:55:21,187
Move! Go!

544
00:55:28,344 --> 00:55:31,119
Let's go, move!

545
00:55:43,877 --> 00:55:46,003
I'm getting tired of you
pointing that thing at me.

546
00:55:46,681 --> 00:55:48,781
-Are you okay?
-Never better.

547
00:55:48,782 --> 00:55:50,051
It looks like we've lost the orb.

548
00:55:53,117 --> 00:55:56,219
Actually you don't think I'd go
vaulting in the thin air for nothing, do you?

549
00:55:56,219 --> 00:55:57,946
I've put a tracer on the crate.

550
00:56:01,099 --> 00:56:01,940
Got it!

551
00:56:02,025 --> 00:56:03,372
Look!

552
00:56:07,820 --> 00:56:08,702
Impressive!

553
00:56:13,067 --> 00:56:17,577
[Hong Kong]

554
00:56:37,351 --> 00:56:41,563
Our weapons...in the middle of the city, no way.

555
00:56:41,936 --> 00:56:44,193
He must have dumped that in the crater

556
00:56:44,587 --> 00:56:45,502
No, it's here

557
00:56:47,457 --> 00:56:48,693
One of the buildings?

558
00:56:50,275 --> 00:56:50,829
No.

559
00:56:52,830 --> 00:56:54,535
It's exactly where we're standing.

560
00:57:00,295 --> 00:57:03,188
There's part of me that always
allow for the possibility

561
00:57:03,189 --> 00:57:05,617
that Pandora's Box was just a legend.

562
00:57:06,493 --> 00:57:08,450
But now I know it's there.

563
00:57:14,355 --> 00:57:15,461
She escaped.

564
00:57:16,362 --> 00:57:18,092
She has no idea where we are.

565
00:57:18,492 --> 00:57:19,991
We take no chances.

566
00:57:20,775 --> 00:57:24,745
Have everything we need
to manufacture an antidote transferred to the jet.

567
00:57:28,561 --> 00:57:30,991
I need an orb for two people

568
00:57:31,205 --> 00:57:33,135
Mid city, soon.

569
00:57:35,287 --> 00:57:36,515
What? Are you crazy?

570
00:57:39,484 --> 00:57:40,243
Who is that?

571
00:57:40,570 --> 00:57:41,460
Piece of cake

572
00:58:49,398 --> 00:58:51,129
Wang Jie, come in.

573
00:58:55,913 --> 00:58:56,908
Hello.

